OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FITV News Meridian has interviewed 100
OL,7,Fveterans up and down the country as
OL,8,Fpart of our coverage of the 80th
OL,9,Fanniversary of D-Day.
OL,11,FLed by our reporter Derek Johnson, he
OL,12,Fand camera operator Siobhan Hart,
OL,13,Fworked tirelessly to capture the
OL,14,Fstories of those involved in D-Day, to
OL,15,Fensure they are never forgotten. You
OL,16,Fcan find all of them on this special
OL,17,FITV News website.
