OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FFor 15 years, Derek and Shiv have been
OL,7,Ftravelling to the beaches, memorials
OL,8,Fand cemeteries of Normandy for ITV
OL,9,FNews Meridian.
OL,11,FBoth have covered events commemorating
OL,12,FD-Day, the Allied invasion of occupied
OL,13,FEurope in 1944 in which 156,000 troops
OL,14,Fcrossed the English Channel by air and
OL,15,Fsea in a single day and landed in
OL,16,FFrance.
