OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FTo mark 80 years, Shiv wanted to go
OL,7,Ffurther than ITV News Meridian has
OL,8,Fever gone before, and, with the help
OL,9,Fof colleagues Kate Taylor and Sandor
OL,10,FTaylor, tracked down more than 80
OL,11,Fveterans, some of whom had never
OL,12,Fbefore told their stories.
OL,14,FThe idea was to ensure that their
OL,15,Fstories would be told 'in full', not
OL,16,Fcut down to fit into a 30-minute
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
