OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThis coincided with the launch of
OL,7,FITV's streaming platform, ITVX, which
OL,8,Fallows regional news teams to publish
OL,9,Flong-form, bespoke journalism, making
OL,10,Fit all possible.
OL,12,FFor more than a year Derek and Shiv
OL,13,Fhave given up their own time to make
OL,14,Fthis project possible, and it has all
OL,15,Fbeen skilfully edited by ITV News
OL,16,FMeridian's James Tee, who volunteered
OL,17,Fto take on the enormous task.
