OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThe living link to D-Day and the
OL,7,FNormandy Landings is fast
OL,8,Fdisappearing. To be a veteran, you
OL,9,Fhave to be at least in your late 90s,
OL,10,Fand many are now too frail to receive
OL,11,Fvisitors or speak at length or at all
OL,12,Fabout their experiences.
OL,14,FDerek and Shiv knew that they were the
OL,15,Famong the last ones who could record
OL,16,Fthe memories of those who fought in
OL,17,FWorld War Two, and set out to find
OL,18,Fwhat they thought would be a handful
OL,19,Fof veterans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
