OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThey were wrong about that. In the
OL,7,Fyear from June 2023, they tracked down
OL,8,Fveteran after veteran, and not just
OL,9,Fthe ones on the front lines.
OL,11,FITV News Meridian found men who were
OL,12,Fin combat and women who drove the
OL,13,Finvasion forward. They were found via
OL,14,Fthe many groups and charities
OL,15,Fdedicated to helping them in their
OL,16,Ftwilight years.
OL,18,FMore were then found through word of
OL,19,Fmouth, interested parties and by
OL,20,Ftrawling through websites and online
OL,21,Farticles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
