OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FIn the end, they weren't able to keep
OL,7,Fevery single word from every single
OL,8,Fveteran. Some people understandably
OL,9,Fdid not tell their stories from start
OL,10,Fto finish, diverted and digressed and
OL,11,Ffocused on some episodes rather than
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,FSo they have been edited down and they
OL,15,Feach run from a few minutes to more
OL,16,Fthan half an hour. The only voices you
OL,17,Fhear are those of the veterans.
OL,19,FThey are available on a dedicated ITV
OL,20,Fwebsite, where they will remain long
OL,21,Fafter that living link disappears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
