OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FIt is not military history. Not a
OL,7,Fstory about ranks and regiments,
OL,8,Ftactics, strategy and weaponry.
OL,10,FIt is the testimony of people who
OL,11,Flived through extraordinary times, did
OL,12,Ftheir duty, and somehow came out the
OL,13,Fother side.
OL,15,FSoon along with museums, artefacts and
OL,16,Fhistoric sites, the stories collected
OL,17,Fby Derek and Shiv will be all that we
OL,18,Fhave left, but their efforts mean they
OL,19,Fwill never be forgotten.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
